originalText.text: Dr. Sarah Pinkhasov is by far the best optometrist in Manhattan. She is so knowledgable and VERY patient (take it from a person that asks the doc 100 questions and needs to understand everything being done to them). She explained everything so thoroughly and made me feel SO comfortable and not rushed during the entire encounter. In addition to doing a full eye exam, she also addressed my acute eye concern. She was able to quickly find the root of the issue and gave me a treatment option that relieved all of my symptoms. I'm so thankful to Dr. Pinkhasov!! Will be telling all my friends and family about her!!
